self.pet_tools.setter(pet_name='fido', pet_desc='sleeper')
self.pet_tools.setter(pet_name='ralf', pet_desc='dribbler')

pets = self.pet_tools.lister()

for pet in pets:

    assert pet.pet_name in ['fido', 'ralf', 'gina']
